org.afplib.afplib

Interface CFIRG

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CFIRGImpl

    public interface CFIRG
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'CFIRG'.

    The following features are supported:

    • FCS Name
    • CP Name
    • SV Size
    • SH Scale
    • Reserved
    • Section

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getCFIRG()
